ught areas and intensity on$\backslash$nagriculture according to field survey result. In the future,$\backslash$nagricultural drought will be estimated in terms of water budget$\backslash$ncombining RS and meteorological data and compared to NDVI-based approach$\backslash$nfor developing early drought warning system.},
